		"name": "Spring AI LangGraph Self-RAG",
		"description": "Self-RAG pipeline: chat, document ingestion, health.\n\nПеред запуском:\n  docker compose up -d\n  ./gradlew bootRun\n\nПеременная base_url = http://localhost:8080 (Collection Variables).",
